<section id="element_caution">
    <title>caution</title>
    <sectioninfo>
        <revhistory>
            <revision>
                <date>2010-11-19</date>
                <author><firstname>Arsi</firstname><surname>Atomi</surname></author>
                <revremark>Initial draft</revremark>
            </revision>
        </revhistory>
    </sectioninfo>
    <para>Caution is an admonition, usually set off from main text.</para>
    <para>Caution is meant to imply reader of the possibility of harm. For example: <sgmltag>caution</sgmltag> could imply harm to equipment while <sgmltag>warning</sgmltag> could imply harm to a person.</para>
    <para>Differences between admonitions are not defined in DocBook.</para>
    <para>Caution requires <sgmltag>para</sgmltag> or other elements for displaying any text.</para>
    <note>
        <title>Source</title>
        <para>DocBook: The Definitive Guide : <ulink url="http://www.docbook.org/tdg/en/html/caution.html">http://www.docbook.org/tdg/en/html/caution.html</ulink></para>
    </note>
    <section>
        <title>caution in db2xhtml Library</title>
        <para>Style at <filename>~css/block.css</filename> element div.e_caution {}</para>
        <para>Processing at <filename>~xsl/elements/block/caution.xsl</filename></para>
    </section>
    <section>
        <title>Example of caution</title>
        <para>Example how db2xhtml Library presents <sgmltag>caution</sgmltag>.</para>
        <para>Basic use of caution with title</para>
        <caution>
            <title>Caution title</title>
            <para>This is a caution example.</para>
        </caution>
        <para>XML lines</para>
        <programlisting><![CDATA[<caution>
    <title>Caution title</title>
    <para>This is a caption example</para>
</caution>]]></programlisting>
        <para>Also, caution can have many different elements inside</para>
        <para>Here's example with <sgmltag>orderedlist</sgmltag></para>
        <caution>
            <orderedlist>
                <listitem><para>First item</para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>Second item</para></listitem>
            </orderedlist>
        </caution>
        <para>And XML lines</para>
        <programlisting><![CDATA[<caution>
            <orderedlist>
                <listitem><para>First item</para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>Second item</para></listitem>
            </orderedlist>
</caution>]]></programlisting>
    </section>
